<br>
On DRo I figure it as about a 20-hour process for most guilds without a bridge, and I charge 30k for the bridge up.  Takes an hour or two to get everyone up.  So you're basically saving 18+ people about eighteen hours for that cost.  You can, at times, find prices cheaper than this - though I almost paid 50k for the service myself before I discovered the guild wanted to tackle Sky just for the heck of it.  <br>
<br>
You can also team up with other magicians in your guild/circle of friends, and split the cost.<br>
